Every time I come to you with new references, new examples, new transcripts - and it's all going to be around [PROJECT NAME] - I want you to look at this .prd file and then help me reproduce new HTMLs with the exact same:
- Interface layout
- Navigation style
- Logos and branding
- Fonts and colors
- Component styles

So I have consistency when working with my team.</code>
                        </div>

                        <h4>Using an Example to Create a PRD</h4>
                        <p>If you have an HTML you love (that you made before or found somewhere), drag it into your examples folder and tell Claude:</p>

